exceptions.tactic: assert (forall x, f x x = true) by (intro; apply surjective_pairing; reflexivity).
exceptions.exn: In environment X : Type f : X -> X -> bool g : surjective f x : X Unable to unify "?M1669 = (fst ?M1669, snd ?M1669)" with "f x x = true".

original: intros X f g. assert (forall x, f x x = true) by (intro; apply surjective_pairing; reflexivity). assert (forall x y, f x y = true \/ f x y = false) by decide equality. assert (forall x y, f x y = true -> x = y) by (intros ? ? ?; apply (H0 x y) in H2; destruct H2; auto). destruct (g tt) as [x y]. specialize (H5 x y). destruct H5; [ symmetry in H6 | idtac ]; apply H3 in H6; subst. intro. assert (H6 := H0 x y). destruct H6. apply H4 in H6. subst. apply H2. reflexivity.
